{{!
    @template local_excursions/activityform_approvals

    View for the approvals section of the activity form.
}}
<div class="approvals">
    {{>local_excursions/activityform_approvals_status}}
    {{>local_excursions/activityform_approvals_notices}}
    {{>local_excursions/activityform_approvals_workflow}}
    <div class="reply-form">
        <textarea class="reply-comment form-control" rows="4" spellcheck="true" placeholder="Add a comment"></textarea>
        <a href="#" id="btn-postcomment" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
    </div>
    <div class="comments"></div>

{{#statushelper.isapproved}}
    <div style="padding: 10px;">
    
      <div>
        <strong>Venue Booking</strong>
        <p>Have you secured a venue? Begin by confirming availability and booking through <a target="_blank" href="https://sobs.com.au/ui/login.php?schoolid=728">SOBS Primary</a> or <a target="_blank" href="https://sobs.com.au/ui/login.php?schoolid=157">SOBS Senior</a>, ensuring your reservation includes time for setup and pack-down. 
          If you’re booking the Snow Concert Hall, please complete the information that’s required in SOBS. 
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Catering Requirements</strong>
        <p>
          If your activity requires catering, please complete the <a target="_blank" href="https://infiniti.canberragrammar.org.au/Infiniti/Produce/launch.aspx?id=db4a01bf-5152-46e3-b345-6a560946de3e&portal=1">Catering Request Form</a>. 
        </p>
        <p>
          If you’re booking the Snow Concert Hall, please complete the information that’s required in SOBS. 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Logistical Support</strong>
        <p>
          For any logistical support, such as event setup, or equipment needs, submit a request through the <a target="_blank" href="https://support.cgs.act.edu.au/">Property and Facilities Support Desk link</a>. As these requests are supported by different teams, can you please put in separate tickets for 
        <ul>
          <li>Cleaning (Please specify whether the event is intended for external participants, including parents. This information is essential to ensure our spaces are appropriately presented for any external visitors) </List.Item>
          <li>Event setup and pack-down requirements, with times </li>
          <li>Equipment needed. </li>
        </ul>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>IT Support </strong>
        <p>
          For technical assistance, including audio-visual needs, doors or room access (SALTO), access control support, submit a ticket through the <a target="_blank" href="https://support.cgs.act.edu.au/">Ed Tech Support Desk link</a>. 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Marketing, Design, and Communications</strong>
        <p>
          For graphic design, communications (such as CGS Connect news and announcements), photography, or online RSVP/payment system (Humanitix), submit a ticket via the <a target="_blank" href="https://support.cgs.act.edu.au/">Marketing, Graphic Design and Events Support Desk link</a>. If you need event management support, select "Events" in the drop-down menu to notify the Events Manager and team. 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Student Projects</strong>
        <p>
          If this is a student-led project and you are the supervising staff member, direct students to raise requests via the <a target="_blank" href="https://support.cgs.act.edu.au/">Student Projects Support Desk link </a>. These steps will help ensure thorough preparation for your event, covering all aspects from venue to support services. 
        </p>
      </div>
    
    
    </div>
    {{/statushelper.isapproved}}

</div>